<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-08-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-08-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="51" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d51">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">724.3415/1999: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Commission of
                                        Neutrals</gloss> to the Paraguayan Minister for Foreign
                                    Affairs (<persName corresp="#p_AH1" type="to">Arbo</persName>)</hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Translation]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-08-10">August 10,
                                        1932</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>With reference our cable 8th instant Bolivia informs us that “we
                                suspended hostilities several days ago” and that “hostilities
                                suspended temporarily.”</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_SHL1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Henry L. Stimson</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State of the United States</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_LTF1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Fabio Lozano T.</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="italic">Minister of Colombia</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_RJ2">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">José Richling</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="italic">Chargé d’Affaires of Uruguay</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_BJT1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">José T. Barón</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="italic">Chargé d’Affaires of Cuba</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_HHP1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">P. Herrera de Huerta</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="italic">Chargé d’Affaires of Mexico</hi>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>